The script CVK8SDiscoverDB.sh can be used to auto-detect the presence of mysql and postgresql databases inside the pods running on the kubernetes cluster.
The script will create the CVTask and CVTaskSet custom resource yamls that can be used for application consistent backups.

Syntax:

CVK8SDiscoverDB.sh --namespace <namespace name> --db <database name>

Example

CVK8SDiscoverDB.sh --namespace all --db mysql,postgres
